clinical_particulars.therapeutic_indications: For treatment of non Hodgkin s lymphoma CD20 positive follicular

contraindications.pharmacodynamics: Tositumomab binds to the CD20 antigen which is predominantly expressed on mature B cells and on 90 of B cell non Hodgkin s lympohomas The antibody leads to selective killing of B cells
